text: Hsieh Cheng-peng and Yang Tsung-hua were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Marco Chiudinelli and Teymuraz Gabashvili won the title after defeating Ruan Roelofse and Yi Chu-huan 6–1, 6–3 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw * Qualifying Draw Gimcheon Open ATP Challenger - Doubles 2017 Doubles
